This is a readme file for the college fantasy football program

The program is designed to automate the process of retrieving player and team stats from espn, analyze, 
and distribute points accordingly.

Goals of this program:
--Retrieve player and team stats from espn by web scraping
--Store stats in a database
--Track fantasy teams
--Track fantasy rosters weekly lineup
--Allocate points weekly
--Display standings and corresponding stat breakdown
--Maintain scoring for each stat category

Stretch goals:
--Track stats real time